  abstract={According to the characteristics of the communication protocol of the electrical information acquisition system, an extension scheme of the communication protocol of the electrical information acquisition system supporting the unstructured data transmission is proposed. First of all, extend the length domain of application layer protocol DL/T 698.45 and some attributes and methods of file block transmission management object, extend the broadcast command and event reporting command of interface protocol Q/GDW 1376.2. Secondly, the long frame mode and multicast frame mode are used in the remote and local transmission processes, and the key parameters in the communication protocol are analyzed and determined. Finally, the feasibility of the scheme is verified by the time-consuming test file upgrade. This solution is useful for the development of unstructured data transmission protocol of electrical information acquisition system.},
